than ask you to come back.

06:18.127 --> 06:19.837
See you soon, Joelma.

06:24.258 --> 06:27.053
My bad, Paulão.
It's all going to Save the Bees.

06:27.136 --> 06:29.597
He doesn't deserve you!
He has someone else.

06:29.680 --> 06:31.015
