has been gossiping about it.

06:33.643 --> 06:35.561
Let's go, kids! It's over.

06:37.313 --> 06:38.981
Cindy, cape.

06:39.398 --> 06:42.068
Brandon, boot. And the other one.

06:42.151 --> 06:43.319
Tiara?

06:45.279 --> 06:47.448
Got the sneakers? Where are they?

06:49.158 --> 06:50.451
[Samantha] I want to go now.

06:51.369 --> 06:52.954
Come on. Let's go.

06:53.037 --> 06:54.497
[male] Help me, kids!

06:54.580 --> 06:57.333
-[Ciggy] Help me get this off!
-[Cindy] It's stuck.

07:00.461 --> 07:02.547
Everyone gets a parking ticket here.

07:02.630 --> 07:03.881
Are you working here now?

07:03.965 --> 07:06.551
No, I already told your co-worker
this is a TV costume.

07:06.634 --> 07:08.302
Get out... Samantha?

07:08.386 --> 07:09.720
Since I was five.

07:09.804 --> 07:12.557
I can't believe this.
My mother was crazy about you.

07:12.640 --> 07:15.309
She named me after you,
but I'm Symantha with a Y.

07:15.393 --> 07:17.103
[laughing] How cool.

07:17.186 --> 07:20.022
But if you'll excuse me,
I'm leaving work, you know?

07:20.106 --> 07:21.607
You're working! That's great.

07:21.691 --> 07:25.153
It's tough out here. The Internet, apps.
Streets are dead.

07:25.903 --> 07:28.072
-Can you take a photo with me?
-Of course.

07:31.492 --> 07:32.743
[shutter clicks]

07:32.827 --> 07:35.621
Let's see. I've one eye that opens
less than the other one.

07:36.831 --> 07:39.208
-[hooker sighs]
-You don't look good?

07:39.292 --> 07:41.252
Me, no, I look great.

07:41.335 --> 07:42.837
[shouting]

07:42.920 --> 07:46.424
Who's the dirty old man
who farted in here?

07:46.507 --> 07:48.426
[laughing]

07:48.926 --> 07:49.844
Samantha?

07:49.927 --> 07:50.928
[together] Yes?

07:51.012 --> 07:54.390
He is speaking to me. Excuse me now.
Nice to meet you.

07:54.474 --> 07:55.683
-Bye!
-Bye!

07:55.933 --> 07:57.477
[sighs] Samantha...

07:57.560 --> 07:59.437
we've been through worse.

07:59.645 --> 08:02.690
-Remember that reality show?
-It was the ostrich's fault, Cig.

08:02.773 --> 08:05.318
[laughing] I know, princess.

08:06.152 --> 08:07.278
Oh...

08:07.987 --> 08:10.198
It's going to be all right, OK?

08:12.283 --> 08:13.451
[he kisses]

08:16.412 --> 08:17.538
Let's go, children!

08:17.622 --> 08:18.789
Let's go!

08:19.290 --> 08:22.627
-[computer game beeps]
-[children laugh]

08:23.794 --> 08:25.546
-[Brandon] That's so funny.
-Brandon.

08:25.630 --> 08:26.839
-Take this.
-[Brandon] OK.

08:26.923 --> 08:28.591
[whispering] Thank you.

08:31.302 --> 08:33.304
-There's something wrong here.
-What?

08:34.096 --> 08:36.307
[Samantha] What's going on?
Kids, lock the doors!

08:36.390 --> 08:38.183
-Lock the doors! Lock them.
-Mom?

08:38.476 --> 08:40.937
-[Samantha] Dodoi?
-[Cindy] Dad?

08:41.020 --> 08:42.730
[people shouting]

08:42.813 --> 08:44.607
[shouting]

08:46.317 --> 08:48.694
Brandon, I'm here. I'm here! Hold my hand.

08:50.655 --> 08:52.073
What the hell?

08:52.823 --> 08:54.158
[Samantha] Son, stay calm.

08:54.242 --> 08:55.409
[kids scream]

08:55.493 --> 08:59.330
It's over, calm down.
Let's get out of the car. Come on.

08:59.789 --> 09:00.998
[door opens]

09:03.042 --> 09:05.002
No! Turn it off! They'll see me.

09:05.753 --> 09:07.255
What are you doing here?

09:07.338 --> 09:08.714
Dad!

09:09.340 --> 09:11.425
-I'm out!
-Did you escape from prison?

09:11.509 --> 09:13.135
-Will we be arrested?
-Calm down.

09:13.219 --> 09:14.220
I'm free!

09:14.303 --> 09:16.138
[Samantha] What do you mean free?

09:16.222 --> 09:17.682
It's been 12 years, Samantha!

09:17.765 --> 09:21.060
-There's a guy climbing on the car!
-It's because Dad is famous.

09:21.143 --> 09:23.396
No, it's just that Brazilians
have a short memory.

09:23.479 --> 09:25.022
[Brandon] He's getting naked!

09:25.106 --> 09:27.149
He tattooed Dad's face on his butt!

09:27.233 --> 09:28.734
These people are insane.

09:29.110 --> 09:31.487
There's a pregnant man
saying the baby is mine!

09:31.571 --> 09:33.864
I was in prison,
how could I get someone pregnant?

09:35.491 --> 09:37.910
Kids, you're going to bed early today, OK?

09:37.994 --> 09:40.121
I need to have a little chat
with your dad.

09:40.204 --> 09:43.749
-But it's still midnight.
-We can make an exception. Go on.

09:43.833 --> 09:45.293
Give Dad a kiss.

09:45.751 --> 09:46.919
[kissing]

09:48.462 --> 09:50.423
[Dodoi] And you, come here.

09:53.134 --> 09:54.468
Aren't you happy to see me?

09:54.552 --> 09:57.680
I was last happy to see you
when you signed the divorce papers.

09:59.056 --> 10:03.227
Take it, my love.
And stop crying, for Christ's sake.

10:03.311 --> 10:04.812
[baby cries]

10:05.563 --> 10:08.065
[Cindy] Mommy, is Daddy
coming to live with us?

10:08.149 --> 10:10.359
No. Daddy is spending Christmas with us.

10:10.443 --> 10:12.111
We came to surprise him.

10:12.194 --> 10:14.447
Is he a gift from Santa?

10:14.530 --> 10:16.574
No, baby. Santa Claus isn't real.

10:16.657 --> 10:17.908
Look, look...

10:18.409 --> 10:20.244
[gate opens]

10:21.495 --> 10:23.122
[Samantha] Now. It's Daddy!

10:23.205 --> 10:25.458
[tires screech]

10:25.541 --> 10:28.127
[Dodoi laughs]

10:28.210 --> 10:30.963
[Dodoi] Here we go, let's drink!

10:32.548 --> 10:33.716
[baby screams]

10:33.799 --> 10:36.927
-I didn't see you, I told you.
-[Samantha] Yeah, right.

10:37.011 --> 10:39.221
-I have changed.
-Say it to your pals.

10:39.305 --> 10:42.058
It was the drink. I quit drinking.

10:42.141 --> 10:43.434
That thing is evil.

10:43.517 --> 10:45.519
I married you while you were in prison.

10:45.603 --> 10:48.481
We had two kids when your life was a mess.

10:48.564 --> 10:50.775
I stood by your side
when no one else wanted to.

10:51.942 --> 10:54.487
[people shouting outside]

10:56.906 --> 11:00.201
Mom, the samba school is outside!
Can I go out and dance?

11:00.284 --> 11:01.452
Go to bed, Brandon!

11:02.662 --> 11:04.080
Go to Rio, Dodoi.

11:04.163 --> 11:07.625
-Look at your pals partying outside.
-I don't want that, Samantha.

11:07.708 --> 11:11.545
I was thinking about buying a ranch
in a place that no one knows us.

11:12.213 --> 11:13.798
Breakfast in bed every day,

11:13.881 --> 11:15.758
orange juice, delicious papayas...

11:16.133 --> 11:19.428
I'm a family man.
The perfect husband, sweetie.

11:19.512 --> 11:23.599
The next time you call me sweetie,
you know what'll happen to you?

11:23.682 --> 11:25.726
-I'll cut off your balls.
-[Dodoi grunts]

11:25.810 --> 11:28.479
[Samantha] Are you kidding me?
Did you eat shit?

11:28.854 --> 11:31.065
You and me, in a little ranch, my dear...

11:31.148 --> 11:35.111
-Now that my life is great?
-I have the right to stay with my kids.

11:35.194 --> 11:37.321
I don't need you, Dodoi!

11:38.906 --> 11:41.242
Come on! Get out of here.

11:41.325 --> 11:44.286
-[people shouting]
-[cameras click]

11:49.959 --> 11:52.420
Send these people away, please.

11:59.510 --> 12:02.555
Calm down, people!

12:03.013 --> 12:05.933
I will talk to everybody.
Good evening, people.

12:06.392 --> 12:09.061
-Everybody from the press, OK?
-Where is Dodoi?

12:09.145 --> 12:11.897
Dodoi is really tired.
He sent me to speak to you.

12:11.981 --> 12:15.276
I sincerely wish you respected my family.

12:15.359 --> 12:17.027
[woman] Forget this bitch, Dodoi!

12:17.111 --> 12:18.654
Keep it to yourself, my dear.

12:18.737 --> 12:20.281
[laughing]

12:20.364 --> 12:21.949
[reporter] You two dating again? [woman] Why did you stop singing?

12:23.701 --> 12:27.329
I've never stopped singing.
I am a slave for my fans.

12:27.413 --> 12:30.541
[cheering]

12:33.002 --> 12:35.212
[woman] Will you never be famous again?

12:35.296 --> 12:39.508
-Global warming: myth or reality?
-[man] You giving him a second chance?

12:39.592 --> 12:41.469
[man] Inseminate me, Samantha!

12:49.059 --> 12:51.604
Tonight you'll sleep here on the couch.

12:51.687 --> 12:53.981
Tomorrow you'll look for a place to stay.

12:54.064 --> 12:56.233
-What did you say?
-What they wanted to hear.

12:56.317 --> 12:57.693
Why haven't they left?

12:58.861 --> 13:00.446
Because they've just arrived.

13:02.000 --> 13:08.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

13:23.219 --> 13:26.597
Samantha, give back the man's leg.
The show will start!

13:26.680 --> 13:28.349
[woman] You're singing together.

13:28.432 --> 13:30.559
He's our guest, Samantha!

13:30.643 --> 13:33.687
Samantha, this is not a joke.
You're going to ruin everything!

13:34.313 --> 13:35.231
[chuckles]

13:43.364 --> 13:46.450
Take me home, take me to school,

13:46.534 --> 13:49.078
