13:55.793 --> 13:58.379
[announcer] <i>Available in Japanese</i>
<i>and Madagascan versions.</i>

14:01.257 --> 14:04.385
[people shouting outside]

14:22.444 --> 14:25.072
People need you.

14:25.155 --> 14:28.951
It's you they look for
when the sky seems to be sad!

14:34.665 --> 14:37.501
[doorbell rings]

14:39.211 --> 14:43.257
Hey, sweetie! You're pretty today! Eh?

14:45.175 --> 14:46.010
Where is she?

14:46.093 --> 14:48.846
Come in, but keep quiet
because my dad is sleeping.

14:51.724 --> 14:52.850
Who is it?

14:55.561 --> 14:57.730
What a surprise, Joelma!

14:57.813 --> 14:58.898
Life is crazy, right?

14:58.981 --> 15:01.692
You're doing it wrong. What did we agree?

15:01.775 --> 15:03.736
Stop the bullshit, I have knee implants!

15:03.819 --> 15:06.405
